<ChatBot
  steps={[
    {
      id: "1",
      message: "What number I am thinking?",
      trigger: "2",
    },
    {
      id: "2",
      options: [
        {
          value: 1,
          label: "Number 1",
          trigger: "4",
        },
        {
          value: 2,
          label: "Number 2",
          trigger: "3",
        },
        {
          value: 3,
          label: "Number 3",
          trigger: "3",
        },
      ],
    },
    {
      id: "3",
      message: "Wrong answer, try again.",
      trigger: "2",
    },
    {
      id: "4",
      message: "Awesome! You are a telepath!",
      end: true,
    },
  ]}
/>;
